Quadding pet, hitting for up to 250 a hit (high end).  That's 1k per quad max at about 18 delay (give or take).  Thats a little over 3k damage per tic which is about 500DPS for the pet, not including procs and such.  Now throw in mage nuke damage.  Now lets throw in flurries...
<br />

<br />
Low end...  150 hit * 4 = 600 per quad.  18 delay or so, a little over 1800 per tic =  around 300DPS from pet without spells/procs/flurries.  Again, add in mage nukes and what does that equal, shanre?
